dct_title_s: The harbour of San Francisco, Nueva California
dct_description_sm: by Captn. F. W. Beechey, R.N.F.R.S. 1827, & 8 ; J. & C. Walker sculpt.
Relief shown by hachures, spot heights, and pictorially, and depths by bathymetric soundings.
Bar scale on inset map given in "Nautic Miles."
Shows topography, drainage, vegetation, ranchos, missions, routes.
Description of tides beneath title; descriptive text throughout.
Inset map: The entrance of San Francisco, harbour.
Profile views: Table Hill -- Clara Mt. -- Punta de los Reyes -- Farallones -- Entrance to San Francisco -- Marks for the Blossom Rock.
